text: Pleiospermium longisepalum (also known as Banguey Island orangeaster) is a species of plant in the family Rutaceae. It is endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sabah. ==References== * ==External links== * longisepalum Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Flora of Sabah Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
